milestones.description: Gary Kirsten and Neil McKenzie's 205-run partnership is SA's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 179 between Kallis and Gibbs
This is the highest match aggregate (500) involving teams South Africa & Kenya in ODIs
South Africa's 209-run win against Kenya is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 202-run win against Kenya

stories.title: South Africa crush Kenya by 208 runs
stories.summary: South Africa swept to an overwhelming 208-run victory over Kenya at Newlands on Monday night, underlining the difference in quality between the two teams, but all is not lost for the Kenyans who meet India in what has effectively become the Standard
